<p><span style='font-family:Consolas,monospace;background:#f4f0eb;padding:1px 4px'>`</span> Inscription programme A → [pas de lien] → Inscription programme B ↓                                        ↓ Clé interne A                            Clé interne B ↓                                        ↓ Prime versée                             Prime versée (?) ↓                                        ↓ [Aucune vue consolidée Cabinet] <span style='font-family:Consolas,monospace;background:#f4f0eb;padding:1px 4px'>`</span></p>
